snippet.title: Lost in Play Trailer
snippet.description: Lost in Play is a game about a brother and sister on an imagination-fueled journey back home. Along the way they'll encounter magnificent creatures like a giant stork, magical seaweed, friendly frogs, and traveling goblins. http://s.team/a/1328840
